txt.en: Defeat many Primordial Wraths in Skirmishes.\nThis deed will only be advanced by Lieutenants that do not appear grey to your character, they must be around the same level as you are.
Defeat many Primordial Wraths in Skirmishes
The Primordial Wrath of Morgoth lingers still, sucking the resolve from the limbs of those it comes in contact with.
